{"tid":2249355,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅家聰指深港「爭生意」難融合","createTime":"2020-10-19T09:37:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T09:40:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3b9ef29b754c7ac38c89c2e8681101a9e8a3039a","tid":2249355,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:37:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/CEHMGS4LC5D7FDOCDIQ7NYAEK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FCEHMGS4LC5D7FDOCDIQ7NYAEK4%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Zr%2FszHQdc4%2B4ddc640yZrNs%3D&h=79b062f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FCEHMGS4LC5D7FDOCDIQ7NYAEK4%2F&h=39094e86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/CEHMGS4LC5D7FDOCDIQ7NYAEK4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n羅家聰指深港「爭生意」難融合<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ifxJ7Fv_H0noS7WWJYmI6KBjhfM=/1631x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RBRMB4A2JVFITF5TYYHOMF2RCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FifxJ7Fv_H0noS7WWJYmI6KBjhfM%3D%2F1631x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRBRMB4A2JVFITF5TYYHOMF2RCM.jpg&h=fe006e40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■羅家聰<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】國家主席習近平日前在深圳特區建立40周年大會演講，提出要促進內地和香港、澳門融合發展，及積極、深入推進粵港澳大灣區建設，雖然港府認為港、深仍可合作，但有經濟學者指，在外國圍堵中國的大環境下，中國自身難以發展高端科技，香港亦失去作為中國與世界接軌的窗口角色，中港難以再談融合，反而中國被迫發展金融中心，深港只會陷入競爭。<br />\n<br />\n港台節目《城市論壇》昨討論深圳發展及香港定位問題，經濟學者羅家聰認為，深港「唔會點融合得到」，除香港將成本高昂產業。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n羅又指，香港兩大優勢包括作為中外橋樑及金融中心，但當外國不再信任一國兩制之餘，中國在美歐甚至鄰近的日本、。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盧偉國拋錯書包吹捧大灣區<br />\n<br />\n而同場的工程界經民聯立法會議員盧偉國則唱好大灣區發展及深港融合，他以華為、中興及騰訊等公司為例，力撐深圳科技發展成功，又指出無人機生產商大疆、順豐速運及內地首間民辦互聯網銀行微眾等均是港人創辦，認為香港青年不應目光狹隘留港，強調大灣區不止提供資源，更提供市場。不過，另一嘉賓、資訊科技界選委兼元朗區議員王百羽糾正指，大疆創辦人汪滔僅為曾到香港就學內地人。<br />\n<br />\n羅家聰也形容，香港人北上。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iLPD2u-m30vLr_koyZJYsL2BX4U=/1594x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MPMT6QZRI5F3JKTJP4HSHCMX3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiLPD2u-m30vLr_koyZJYsL2BX4U%3D%2F1594x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMPMT6QZRI5F3JKTJP4HSHCMX3M.jpg&h=90366275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■內地提出要促進深港融合，惟羅家聰預料兩地競爭居多。資料圖片"},{"pid":"9ff97317d665cff8014932941ecb46efa16b24fe","tid":2249355,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:40:17.000Z","msg":"樓價高企，市民不能安居樂業<br />\n係香港深圳最失敗既地方"}]}